    "description": "Undefeated Samurai is an exciting new online role-playing metaverse (RPG) that combines an incredible, immersive virtual-reality experience.<br><br>We have created a metaverse where players can socialize with each other while trying to be the one that survives. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795030/extras/f51b7d720dee5ab93e21f7479ebf4168.poster.avif?t=1641502664\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795030/extras/f51b7d720dee5ab93e21f7479ebf4168.webm?t=1641502664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795030/extras/f51b7d720dee5ab93e21f7479ebf4168.mp4?t=1641502664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Undefeated Samurai is a built-for-VR feudal Japan fantasy sandbox with melee combat that is driven by stats and sword fighting that fully utilizes a unique and realistic physics-driven interaction and combat system.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795030/extras/44ae0c8187a49ae27ad0c7d23cb65834.poster.avif?t=1641502664\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795030/extras/44ae0c8187a49ae27ad0c7d23cb65834.webm?t=1641502664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795030/extras/44ae0c8187a49ae27ad0c7d23cb65834.mp4?t=1641502664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In Undefeated Samurai, the combat is limited only by your own creativity. Choose your character, choose your sword, fight your way; Be the undefeated Samurai you always dreamed of becoming!",
